Dexia Plans No Split, Chairman Jean-Luc Dehaene Says

-- B y   F a b i o   B e n e d e t t i - V a l e n t i n i
-- 
2011-09-27T16:41:21Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-27/dexia-plans-no-split-chairman-jean-luc-dehaene-says.html
Dexia SA (DEXB)  doesn’t plan to split,
Chairman Jean-Luc Dehaene said in an e-mailed statement today.  “It is as a whole that the group must manage the heritage
of the past and work to guarantee its future,” Dehaene said.
“The strategic committee and the board of directors will
continue, as they have in the past, to examine various
hypotheses with the aim of strengthening the financial
fundamentals” of Dexia “and to guarantee the development of
its business lines,” the chairman said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Fabio Benedetti-Valentini at 
 fabiobv@bloomberg.net  